{"tid":165128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國億萬富豪洛克菲勒逝世，終年101歲。","createTime":"2017-03-21T06:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T08:09:13.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb35311b93d10450ee3d6db418893575a03b81a","tid":165128,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=214831\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214831&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuQEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=d4703439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D214831&h=828ec04c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=214831</a><br />\n<br />\n洛克菲勒出生顯赫世家，祖父是標準石油公司始創人，他自己是一名銀行家，在哈佛大學畢業後曾任職多間美國大型銀行，退休前是大通曼哈頓銀行的行政總裁及主席，在全球金融事務上舉足輕重。<br />\n<br />\n洛克菲勒亦曾任前總統尼克遜的顧問，曾經到訪北京，與時任總理周恩來會面。<br />\n<br />\n洛克菲勒在其他兄弟姐妹相繼離世後，接手掌管家族財富及慈善事業，估計他的身家最少有三十億美元，他在慶祝一百歲生日時，捐出近一千畝國家公園土地予緬因州政府。<br />\n<br />\n洛克菲勒的發言人表示，他周一在紐約州寓所於睡夢中病逝，終年101歲。"},{"pid":"4c0f7903652da9461772e8997d70b74570b5eb0d","tid":165128,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09782ce95c188669ced222252b3277cbb270c498","tid":165128,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:44:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a3d9e76d50da7e45571a88a57b2d7f749899757","tid":165128,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三十億美金...<br />\n對比起佢啊爺個陣<br />\n都算稀噓</blockquote><br />\n佢：大家咁話"},{"pid":"4b4c8939242c191bbfb14bb232a5ffd4cae0b4be","tid":165128,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:46